{"word":"λιμός","slug":"λιμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λιμός, οῦ, ὁ</el>/<el>ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λοιμός\">λοιμός</a></el>] ‘condition of misery caused by lack of food’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on craving for food <b>hunger <a href='B:490 15:17'>Lk 15:17</a>; <a href='B:520 8:35'>Ro 8:35</a>; <a href='B:540 11:27'>2 Cor 11:27</a>;</b> as serious lack of food causing hunger in a broad area <b>famine <a href='B:480 13:8'>Mk 13:8</a>; <a href='B:490 4:25'>Lk 4:25</a>; <a href='B:490 15:14'>15:14</a>; <a href='B:510 7:11'>Ac 7:11</a>; <a href='B:730 6:8'>Rv 6:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λίμνη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:λίνον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}